
* OPA380 Photovoltaic Amplifier with 12x BPW34 in Series (Voltage Amplifier Mode)
* Simulates weak light conditions with output ~210uV from PD chain
* Voltage amplifier with comparator stage

* Voltage source to simulate photodiode output (replace with behavioral voltage if needed)
VPD PD_IN 0 DC 210uV

* Power supply
VCC VCC 0 DC 3.3V

* Amplifier model (ideal op-amp as placeholder for OPA380, replace with OPA380.lib if available)
* .include OPA380.lib
* XU1 PD_IN 0 OUT VCC 0 OPA380

* Ideal op-amp model (non-inverting amplifier)
EAMP OUT 0 PD_IN 0 1MEG

* Feedback resistors for gain
R1 0 IN- 1k
R2 IN- OUT 100k

* Comparator stage
* Reference voltage
VREF VREF 0 DC 200mV

* Comparator model (ideal)
ECOMP COMP_OUT 0 OUT VREF 1MEG

* Loads
RL1 OUT 0 10k
RL2 COMP_OUT 0 10k

.tran 0 10m
.control
run
plot V(PD_IN) V(OUT) V(COMP_OUT)
.endc
.end
